-amber-400\">+$<!-- -->3</span><span class=\"text-muted-foreground\">/user/mo</span></div><div class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">For <!-- -->50<!-- --> users: +<!-- -->$150<!-- -->/mo</div></div><div class=\"lg:w-2/3 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 bg-white/60 dark:bg-gray-900/40 rounded-lg px-3 py-2.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield h-4 w-4 text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm\">NVD CVE vulnerability scanning (auto-update)</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 bg-white/60 dark:bg-gray-900/40 rounded-lg px-3 py-2.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield h-4 w-4 text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm\">Device-aware CVE applicability filtering</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 bg-white/60 dark:bg-gray-900/40 rounded-lg px-3 py-2.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield h-4 w-4 text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\">